{"tid":1785794,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"靜靜渡過今年聖誕節","createTime":"2019-12-16T16:00:06.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-16T16:21:34.000Z","uid":307504,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"3350bc45ca631af4d588b2d80d94784ff3168408","tid":1785794,"uid":307504,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-16T16:00:06.000Z","msg":"各位手足：<br />\n明白大家很希望過一個快樂聖誕節，<br />\n而我不是在拆毀大家不讓大家過快樂聖誕節，<br />\n只是這場抗爭運動半年了，<br />\n「五大訴求，缺一不可」下，<br />\n只有一項達成，另四項仍未達到目標......<br />\n<br />\n此外，無數手足死傷，至今仍未沉冤得雪，<br />\n香港還未光復，仍走在黑暗中，<br />\n實不應過於舖張慶祝聖誕節，<br />\n也不應製造空間予柒婆政權及中共政權認為香港已平安<br />\n<br />\n......我們可以考慮在各自社區點起燭光，<br />\n或是亮起電話燈，讓逝去義士知道，<br />\n我們沒有因為聖誕節忘記他們，<br />\n我們沒有忘記傷痕，自私地慶祝聖誕節<br />\n<br />\n光復香港，時代革命"},{"pid":"0b480dc7b429b02782ad58cfb8f883f0c029518e","tid":1785794,"uid":188685,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-16T16:10:06.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">12.22  愛丁堡<br />\n12.21  721五個月 <br />\n12.24 和你shop<br />\n12.24  夜晚尖咀見<br />\n12.31  和你拖<br />\n2020.1.1元旦大遊行</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/X8cUMgZ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FX8cUMgZ.jpg&h=dd131fdc&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/9qF3EB1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F9qF3EB1.jpg&h=981a21a6&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/r5GnaJH.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fr5GnaJH.jpg&h=8d5141c2&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/eeRnaJJ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FeeRnaJJ.jpg&h=513a7d8e&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/FxgqSW3.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FFxgqSW3.jpg&h=2006eaa8&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/sGaZXqr.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FsGaZXqr.